title: 17. The Panic Pandemic: Are You Infected With These 5 Fears?
itunes:title: 17. The Panic Pandemic: Are You Infected With These 5 Fears?
description: It seems everybody these days is infected by fear. The truth is, most people are afraid of the wrong things. In this episode, I share 5 things you absolutely should be afraid of; when you are, fear becomes a motivation—not just to make it through this pandemic, but to succeed in all of life!
